title: Picnic Time's Avalanche 538-38
transcripts: Take your picnic anywhere with the Avalanche picnic cooler on wheels by Picnic Time. This innovative design features deluxe service for four. It has a spacious cooler with a hard shell interior and a 45 can capacity. Made blow molded plastic with thermo-guard insulation. The Avalanche is made of attractive polyester dobie and has a built in trolley with 2 inch easy glide wheels and a thirty nine inch tall telescoping handle. Two carrying candles fastened together for a sturdier grip and the adjustable fully removable shoulder strap adds versatility for attaching other items to the cooler, two open mesh pockets and a secure zipper pocket on the exterior provide more space to carry personal effects. The Avalanche includes four mounting plates, 4 ten ounce tumblers, one stainless steel cheese knife, with wooden handle, four cotton napkins, 1 cotton table cloth, four stainless steel forks knives and spoons, 1 six inch hardwood cutting board, a set of salt and pepper shakers, a bottle stopper, and one stainless steel corkscrew with wooden handle. This dynamic cooler is great for families who love to picnic. No picnic is out of reach for the Avalanche.
